---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import Logo from "../components/Logo.astro";
import Button from "../components/Button.astro";
import VideoEmbed from "../components/VideoEmbed.astro";
import SiteFooter from "../components/SiteFooter.astro";

const testimonials = [
  {
    quote:
      "Synchro Social helped me grow over 300k followers in the first year of working together.",
    name: "Baya Voce",
  },
  {
    quote: "I don't know where I would be without the team at Synchro Social.",
    name: "Jessica Winterstern",
  },
  {
    quote:
      "I had a video reach over 1 million views within the first week of working with Synchro Social.",
    name: "Morgan Burch",
  },
];

const stats = [
  { value: "1B+", label: "Content Views" },
  { value: "$0", label: "Ad Spend" },
  { value: "4M+", label: "Followers Grown" },
];
---

<Layout
  title="AI Clone Content That Grows Your Social Media — Synchro Social"
  description="We build your AI clone that grows your social media without you ever filming again. Made for women who want a content machine — look beautiful, sound authoritative, grow your audience."
  bodyClass="bg-gradient-to-b from-white via-coral-50 to-coral-100"
>
  <!-- Top banner -->
  <div class="bg-coral-gradient px-4 py-2.5 text-center text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider text-white">
    Limited Availability · Apply Now & See If You Qualify
  </div>

  <main>
    <!-- Hero -->
    <section class="mx-auto max-w-4xl px-6 pt-12 pb-10 text-center">
      <Logo tone="coral" href="/" class="mx-auto" />
      <h1
        class="font-display mx-auto mt-9 max-w-3xl text-4xl font-extrabold leading-[1.1] text-ink sm:text-5xl"
      >
        We Build Your <span class="text-coral-500">AI Clone</span> That Grows Your
        Social Media <span class="text-coral-500">Without</span> You Ever Filming Again
      </h1>
      <p class="mx-auto mt-5 max-w-xl text-base text-muted sm:text-lg">
        Made for women who want a content machine that makes you look beautiful,
        sound authoritative, and grow your audience — without ever picking up a
        camera.
      </p>

      <div class="mx-auto mt-10 max-w-2xl">
        <p class="font-display mb-3 text-lg font-bold text-ink">
          How We Grow Your Brand <span class="text-coral-500">— Without Filming</span>
        </p>
        <VideoEmbed
          provider="wistia"
          id="xdui93k7no7yvhl"
          title="How we grow your brand without filming"
          tone="coral"
        />
      </div>

      <div class="mt-9 flex flex-col items-center gap-2">
        <Button href="/call" tone="coral">Schedule a Call</Button>
        <p class="text-xs font-medium uppercase tracking-wider text-muted">
          Limited spots each month · Apply now & book your strategy call
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Testimonials -->
    <section class="mx-auto max-w-5xl px-6 py-12">
      <div class="grid gap-5 sm:grid-cols-3">
        {
          testimonials.map((t) => (
            <figure class="rounded-2xl bg-white p-6 shadow-sm ring-1 ring-coral-100">
              <blockquote class="text-sm leading-relaxed text-ink">
                “{t.quote}”
              </blockquote>
              <figcaption class="mt-4 text-sm font-semibold text-coral-600">
                {t.name}
              </figcaption>
            </figure>
          ))
        }
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Sales letter -->
    <section class="mx-auto max-w-2xl px-6 py-12 text-center">
      <h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-bold text-coral-500">
        I'll be straight with you.
      </h2>
      <div class="mt-6 space-y-5 text-base leading-relaxed text-ink/90">
        <p>
          Most women trying to build something online right now are doing it
          completely backwards. Posting random content hoping something hits.
          Spending thousands of dollars on videographers, makeup and hair, social
          media teams, and then going dark for two weeks because life got in the
          way. Watching other women blow up and wondering "what does she know
          that I don't?"
        </p>
        <p>
          I'll tell you what she knows. She knows that <span class="font-semibold text-coral-500"
            >the most successful women online aren't the most talented</span
          >. They're the most visible. She figured out how to show up
          consistently, professionally, in a way that builds trust before a
          single sales conversation ever happens. And she stopped letting the
          production machine eat her alive.
        </p>
        <p class="font-display text-lg font-bold text-coral-500">
          That's it. That's the whole game.
        </p>
        <p>
          We've watched so many women with genuinely life-changing things to say
          get completely buried online — not because their message wasn't good
          enough, but because the system of content creation was never designed
          for someone running an actual business. It was designed for
          22-year-olds with nothing else on their calendar.
        </p>
        <p>
          You don't have nothing else on your calendar. You have clients. You
          have a life. You have expertise that took years to build. And <span
            class="font-semibold text-coral-500"
            >you deserve a vehicle that actually scales it.</span
          >
        </p>
        <p>
          That's what we built. A photorealistic avatar that looks like you on
          your best day, every day. A full team handling strategy, scripts,
          editing, and posting. <span class="font-semibold text-coral-500"
            >A system where your only job is to say yes.</span
          > We've helped clients rack up over a billion views doing exactly this —
          and not one of them spent a Saturday in a studio wondering if they
          looked tired on camera.
        </p>
        <p>
          This call is for the woman who knows she's leaving clients and revenue
          on the table every week she's not showing up. The woman who's been the
          best-kept secret in her industry for too long.
        </p>
        <p class="font-display text-lg font-bold text-coral-500">
          This is how that changes. And it starts with one conversation.
        </p>
        <p class="font-semibold text-ink">Book the call below.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-9 flex justify-center">
        <Button href="/call" tone="coral">Schedule a Call</Button>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Stats -->
    <section class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-6 pt-4 pb-20">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-3 gap-4">
        {
          stats.map((s) => (
            <div class="rounded-2xl bg-white/70 px-4 py-7 text-center shadow-sm ring-1 ring-coral-100">
              <div class="font-display text-3xl font-extrabold text-ink sm:text-4xl">
                {s.value}
              </div>
              <div class="mt-1 text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide text-muted">
                {s.label}
              </div>
            </div>
          ))
        }
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <SiteFooter tone="coral" />
</Layout>
